title: Taylor Williamson
description: One of Pete's favorite comedians Taylor Williamson (Last Comic Standing, Ferguson, comedy!) is a delightful YMIW guest: funny, thoughtful and super weird. Hear Pete tell Taylor what to call his upcoming CD! Hear Taylor tell jokes he cut from the CD! Hear Katie laugh!! It's a big one. GET INTO IT, YOU WEIRDOS!
